        "client_msg_id": "b29ef1b7-1260-483d-b189-39fd14678b98",
        "text": "What the heck is Slackbot talking about? _Computers are so weird._ So… let's also be weird!!\n\nOn <https:\/\/time.is\/1800_29_October_2025_in_UTC?FoC_Virtual_Costume_Party|Wednesday October 29th>, instead of our usual virtual meetup, we're going to do something special: a *virtual costume party*!\n\nYour \"costume\" can be whatever you want it to be. Got a real halloween costume you want to wear? Go for it! Or, keep it simple and just pick a fun zoom background. Or, do what I'll be doing: set up something wild in OBS that totally changes how you look and\/or sound.\n\nWe'll have some demos at the usual time (assuming anyone signs up — reply in the thread here if interested). But I'll also just keep the zoom call running for a while before and after so folks can drop in and hang out, enjoy each other's costumes, talk about computers, share impromptu demos, and so forth.\n\nI'll see you _scare_!",
        "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "user_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "source_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "user_profile": {
